ActCanadian International Trade Tribunal Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian International Trade Tribunal Procurement Inquiry Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL PROCUREMENT INQUIRY REGULATIONS in order to allow the Canadian International Trade Tribunal to consider and make findings with respect to complaints concerning government procurements that are subject to the terms of the Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA).
